    <text>
        <body>
            <head>Wildest Dreams</head>
            
            <lg n="1" type="verse">
                <l>He said "Let's <del>disappear</del> <add place="above">get out of</add></l>
                <l><del>from here</del> this <placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q3957">town</placeName>"</l>
                <l>Drive out of the <placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q515">city</placeName></l>
                <l><del>'Til the lights burn out</del></l> 
                <l><del>I thought</del> It's okay</l>
                <l>if we never get found</l>
                <l>Live in here forever</l>
                <l>Better keep it to yourself</l>
            </lg>

            <lg n="2" type="pre-chorus">
                <l>A-and you're so tall</l>
                <l>And handsome as hell</l>
                <l>I don't know what you do</l>
                <l>But you're doing it well</l>
                <l>And when we've had</l>
                <l>our very last kiss</l>
                <l>My last request is... <del>Close</del></l>
            </lg>

            <lg n="3" type="chorus">
                <l>Say you'll remember me</l>
                <l>Standing in a <objectName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q200539">nice dress</objectName></l>
                <l>Staring at the <term type="time" ref="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q166564">sunset</term>, babe</l>
                <l>Red <objectName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q15173">lips</objectName> and rosy <objectName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q193858">cheeks</objectName></l>
                <l>Say <del>that this won't be</del></l>
                <l><del>the last time baby</del></l>
                <l>You'll see me again</l>
            </lg>
        </body>
